content:
Configure Commerce with the Enhanced Setup Assistant

Get a more streamlined experience with the revamped Commerce Setup Assistant. The Assistant walks you through basic setup and installs the essential settings and page layouts. If setup fails or only partially completes, the Assistant also provides troubleshooting guidance.

Where: This change applies to B2B Commerce and D2C Commerce in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions.

How: From Salesforce Setup, open the Commerce Setup Assistant, and click Get Started.
title: Streamlining Commerce Setup with Enhanced Assistant
